{
  "stem": "27507.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, finally, it was-- somehow, my uncle Lulek, who was the manager of that shop, of that factory part, decided to take me out, and my mother as well.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were smuggled to the area inside of Warsaw in the beginning of February, '43, I think on the 8th of February.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was possible to get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was physically-- it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But it was possible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You had, again, to bribe the police or the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they-- my uncle, who quite could officially leave to go to get some material for the factory, took me on the cart with him, and explained to the gendarme-- it was all fixed beforehand, of course-- that it's my birthday.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he's going to get me a treat of some kind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so I was allowed to go out of ghetto on this cart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And, of course, I never came back again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And my mother left in the same way, I think a couple of days before me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I don't remember it was couple days before or after.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I then finished in the flat, first in some factory, where probably my uncle had to get these materials, these tissues-- not tissues, clothes, whatever it was that he needed, bales of cloth, or wool.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't know what it was anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Then I stayed in this factory until it was dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
